sequenceDiagram
  actor Customer
  participant API as Order API
  participant DB as PostgreSQL
  participant Relay as Outbox Relay
  participant Broker as Event Broker
  participant Billing

  Customer->>API: POST /deliveries + Idempotency-Key
  API->>DB: Begin transaction
  API->>DB: Insert delivery request
  API->>DB: Insert OrderCreated outbox record
  DB-->>API: Commit
  API-->>Customer: 201 Created
  Relay->>DB: Read unpublished outbox record
  Relay->>Broker: Publish OrderCreated
  Broker->>Billing: Deliver event
  Billing->>Billing: Deduplicate by eventId
  Billing->>DB: Create invoice
